01:13.789 --> 01:16.841
Jim, your ability with the ladies
never ceases to amaze me.

01:16.966 --> 01:18.834
What can I say?
I love women.

01:18.959 --> 01:22.605
This might make me sound like a wuss,
but I get off when they get off.

01:22.773 --> 01:24.566
- Come on!
