bullet lodged in my spine.

10:16.542 --> 10:17.492
I'm bad cop.

10:17.617 --> 10:20.381
No, no, your accident humbled you

10:20.506 --> 10:22.465
and made you grateful
for every day you're alive.

10:22.590 --> 10:24.206
- You're good cop.
- I'm bad cop!

10:24.331 --> 10:27.758
You don't have the guts! I can
bad cop better than you in my sleep.

10:30.843 --> 10:33.991
You wanna go to jail, double-stuff?
Oh, the boys'll love you in there.

10:34.116 --> 10:36.663
They won't leave
one fat fold unviolated.

10:38.851 --> 10:41.342
Still won't talk?
Maybe I'll reach out to a buddy of mine.

10:41.467 --> 10:42.901
Dirty Cop owes me a favor.

10:43.026 --> 10:45.786
In two hours, I can have
a dead baby stuffed with heroin

10:45.911 --> 10:49.521
planted in your mom's car.
Is that what you want, wide load?!

10:51.119 --> 10:53.619
- Put out your hands.
- I made heavy pants!

10:53.744 --> 10:55.541
