10:55.666 --> 10:57.822
You got real pretty hands, fat boy.

10:58.881 --> 11:00.626
Now I'm gonna make you eat 'em!

11:01.884 --> 11:02.967
God, Roger!

11:03.092 --> 11:05.272
All right, all right,
you can be bad cop.

11:05.397 --> 11:07.203
Thank you. That's all I wanted to hear.

11:07.328 --> 11:09.759
I confess!
I went in Hayley's room.

11:09.884 --> 11:12.207
I like to put her toothbrush
in my mouth.

11:12.332 --> 11:15.169
It tastes like mint,
and sometimes I find food.

11:15.381 --> 11:17.002
But what about Hayley's Shuffle?

11:17.423 --> 11:20.202
I don't know. I was just eating
toothbrush corn.

11:20.327 --> 11:21.917
Then the fish scared me away.

11:27.284 --> 11:28.497
Looking good!

11:28.952 --> 11:30.051
Doesn't she?

11:30.456 --> 11:33.023
- Jim! Wait, what are you doing here?
- Didn't I tell you?

11:33.147 --> 11:34.995
Can you get my back, J-dog?

11:35.307 --> 11:36.702
Jim's my backup husband.

11:36.870 --> 11:38.412
- What?!
- I'm honored.

11:38.537 --> 11:40.664
I mean, be sleeping
with your wife someday.

11:40.789 --> 11:43.019
That makes us, like,
brothers or something.

11:43.144 --> 11:46.741
- Would you excuse us for a minute, Jim?
- Sure, I'll just go do my tai-chi.

11:49.391 --> 11:50.864
I see what you're doing here,

11:50.989 --> 11:54.112
