having Meg Penner rub lotion on me.

11:54.312 --> 11:57.343
No, you just laid around her office
for the last ten years,

11:57.468 --> 11:59.428
letting her fingers in your mouth.

11:59.683 --> 12:01.818
I'm just making up for lost time.

12:07.628 --> 12:09.325
I know why you're upset.

12:09.623 --> 12:12.213
Baby, none of this
happens till you're dead.

12:12.821 --> 12:15.271
Oh, God! Jim,
your niece's piano recital!

12:16.270 --> 12:18.317
Grab the cupcakes and let's go!

12:25.034 --> 12:28.379
Damn! Did you see what homeboy
was packing in his Speedo?

12:28.653 --> 12:30.218
I mean, I can't relax.

12:30.343 --> 12:32.597
I'm in an inner tube, in a pool,

12:32.722 --> 12:34.943
with a drink and I can't get right.

12:35.068 --> 12:36.814
Reginald, what are you doing here?

12:36.939 --> 12:39.186
I just got back from a CIA mission.

12:39.429 --> 12:42.175
'Cause, you know,
sometimes I be on missions.

12:42.420 --> 12:44.914
Sometimes I just be
hanging out here at the house.

12:45.039 --> 12:46.383
But more importantly,

12:46.508 --> 12:50.160
what's up with Prince Walnuts
rubbing lotion on your wife?

12:50.633 --> 12:52.218
You better handle your business.

12:52.343 --> 12:54.820
Yeah, I guess I got to break up
with Meg Penner tomorrow.

12:55.510 --> 12:57.189
It's probably for the best.

12:57.314 --> 12:59.432
Man, I hate ending relationships.

12:59.557 --> 13:01.558
