13:30.947 --> 13:32.396
- What was that?
- A wisecrack.

13:32.521 --> 13:34.140
- I'm cracking wise.
- No way!

13:34.265 --> 13:36.788
You can't be bad cop
and do the wisecracks.

13:36.913 --> 13:38.447
I'm doing the wisecracks!

13:39.310 --> 13:43.115
Klaus, you're going to face
the scales of Lady Justice.

13:43.240 --> 13:45.482
