you're on the hook for this one.

13:48.849 --> 13:51.739
Your days of crime are H2 over!

13:51.863 --> 13:54.142
- That doesn't even make sense!
- Fish live in water!

13:54.317 --> 13:55.316
Enough!

13:55.700 --> 13:58.232
I confess.
Just, please, no more puns.

13:58.477 --> 13:59.628
I knew he was lying!

13:59.752 --> 14:02.438
There hasn't been a good article
on hip dysplasia in years.

14:02.682 --> 14:04.487
Look, I did go into Hayley's room.

14:04.612 --> 14:07.603
