you just said?

14:31.032 --> 14:33.120
What are you doing here?
You have an appointment?

14:33.245 --> 14:35.885
No, but you're about
to have a disappointment.

14:36.159 --> 14:39.049
Meg, I've got to break things off.
You can't be my backup wife.

14:39.323 --> 14:40.755
What? That?

14:40.879 --> 14:43.755
For heaven's sakes, I thought
that was some kind of a joke.

14:44.137 --> 14:46.421
And the ego goes into defense mode.

14:48.544 --> 14:50.538
Amazing how the human brain
works, isn't it?

14:51.830 --> 14:53.168
She keeps saying my name.

14:53.803 --> 14:54.963
You got it bad, Meg.

14:55.088 --> 14:57.334
You just need to turn around
and walk away.

14:57.555 --> 14:58.834
But this is my office.

14:59.170 --> 15:01.193
Good, good, throw yourself
into your work.

15:01.318 --> 15:03.560
Now, listen, I'm going to leave,
but...

15:03.685 --> 15:05.196
these little love notes?

15:05.773 --> 15:07.054
Meg, no more of these.

15:07.303 --> 15:10.412
That's an appointment card.
I send them to all my patients.

15:14.591 --> 15:17.144
Now I know it won't be easy,
but try to forget about me.

15:17.269 --> 15:19.515
Do something nice for yourself.
Get a massage.

15:19.640 --> 15:21.687
Go have salad with the girls...

15:22.130 --> 15:25.496
