like this never happened?

15:44.689 --> 15:47.689
- Right!
- That's a big emotional negatory!

15:47.931 --> 15:50.177
- I'm sorry?
- No can do!

15:50.602 --> 15:52.517
I'm in love with your wife!

15:52.914 --> 15:53.738
What?!

15:53.862 --> 15:56.278
She's sexy! She's funny!

15:56.403 --> 15:58.001
My niece loves her...!

15:58.896 --> 16:01.264
